{"tid":1633913,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"是日連登滲透人士風向： 休息","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:45:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T06:47:49.000Z","uid":26015,"like":22,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"96fdd4b1bd02df9650933fafe36bc7b94eef1bad","tid":1633913,"uid":26015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:45:47.000Z","msg":"星期五用緊急法<br />\n接著落黎三日假期 <br />\n其中兩日叫人休息<br />\n目的顯而易見<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就係想大家消化哂緊急法、冷卻之前既憤怒情緒</span></span><br />\n<br />\n講真 如果林奠係今日先宣布用緊急法<br />\n聽日肯定全世界罷工唔撚柒做都似<br />\n佢就係正正唔想見到咁<br />\n就希望大家休息下冷靜下<br />\n聽日繼續如常乖乖咁做港奴 <br />\n唔想你地搞咁多野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />認同<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反對"},{"pid":"0ef50d03ae3d6cefb6b7567c45310b59eca42f89","tid":1633913,"uid":26015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:46:18.000Z","msg":"自推二十五連"},{"pid":"5669b7c872f0f4f3800f0cf07949da93289a936e","tid":1633913,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:46:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bba256186e53efd3f59dfe3000f428c0d54a0341","tid":1633913,"uid":26015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:46:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0374d62d6e541fe5ce90952e69dcf7021e89d6ad","tid":1633913,"uid":26015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:46:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"57e511ae5c38aace131c4b6aa07242f5c58830cc","tid":1633913,"uid":26015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:46:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41e51d7b4a64bcb10baf712ebcd44f33120349b4","tid":1633913,"uid":26015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:47:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e036092c65db18f9cd32bd925f4c56bcbe9d576","tid":1633913,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:47:03.000Z","msg":"唔係休息<br />\n而係繼續要推文宣<br />\n遍地開花<br />\n但不限於勇武<br />\n和理非都可以遍地開花架"},{"pid":"c3b4184cdc5c654dacc7a13ae4289eb93d19dddf","tid":1633913,"uid":266410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:47:22.000Z","msg":"有晒證據可以制裁黑警既POST又無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[真核彈]暗角打鑊2019高清版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ajpHCwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ajpHCwU</a><br />\n(證據確鑿) ■ 黑警再次向市民瘋狂毆打 拳打腳踢!!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629779\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629779</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=996065064074142\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D996065064074142&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4hZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=bb7b04c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=996065064074142</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/fnixt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Ffnixt&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4hZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=b18311a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/fnixt</a>"},{"pid":"0ee4078d770719637a7a08a95eb61ed6779545c9","tid":1633913,"uid":141879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:47:27.000Z","msg":"琴日你覺得有休息到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d2b75acf8dd60a8d4563de318dd81be131e39f","tid":1633913,"uid":167011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:47:54.000Z","msg":"罷工係對個政權最撚有衝擊既抗爭手法，但三罷做左咁撚多次，都係得8.5成功，因為計劃左好撚耐，對香港人黎講，個個都只想被罷工，到呢個地步，你仲想做休息撚，而唔乘勝追擊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但咁撚樣都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係話和理非冇用，但和勇合一係成場運動既關鍵，兩樣一齊做唔撚得？講緊既係，拆鐵係唔撚會影響人權法，或所謂既民意，但對政權、運動係現時有最大既影響力"},{"pid":"2ec27040eaa7331e5320eb07097914409ad4fe40","tid":1633913,"uid":71335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:48:29.000Z","msg":"休息就一定唔係<br />\n勇武都唔可以停 但就唔會再拆野住 過埋人權法先<br />\n私了就無啦 自衛就可以"},{"pid":"e49a417a4b4e5032b0963fe86133c4654f205a12","tid":1633913,"uid":89873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:49:48.000Z","msg":"借個位黎用吓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全港最黃嘅光時網物平台於10月7日上線啦!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629141</a>"},{"pid":"92d1e171533783f8a57016c5cd0d5bcc82afe7d1","tid":1633913,"uid":150083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:51:34.000Z","msg":"今晚一定要遍地開花"},{"pid":"46eb157ea8653f8ebca4ecf97eecbdd0b343b9a1","tid":1633913,"uid":26015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ee4078d770719637a7a08a95eb61ed6779545c9","tid":1633913,"uid":141879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:47:27.000Z","msg":"琴日你覺得有休息到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:52:06.000Z","msg":"星期六啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c5728828b808ab79d1010d9714a18424a9c033d","tid":1633913,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:52:35.000Z","msg":"有時唔洗下下硬打既，轉個方式抗爭都得<br />\n比勇武叉叉電 比文宣組做下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631757</a>"},{"pid":"2445ef2a04f83fe44e48162be1ed91da55cddaf5","tid":1633913,"uid":64744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:52:37.000Z","msg":"呢幾日放假港鐵停駛<br />\n聽日返工港鐵就冇事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好勁嘅風"},{"pid":"0f474f4fc8dafb15fc34100097f90f3dc360c679","tid":1633913,"uid":26015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:53:57.000Z","msg":"勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n幫幫手睇下"},{"pid":"893a3435c2900f70d8a9d8a1061575bed6dc25c9","tid":1633913,"uid":331650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:55:14.000Z","msg":"降吧黑警，仲有條生路俾你同家人<br />\n10/10 deadline<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/ejwexT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/ejwexT</a><br />\n<br />\n囗號其實可以係，叫佢地投降<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n解散警隊，刻不容緩。<br />\n指證黑警，放你一馬。"},{"pid":"c20547b2d11900cecabd1d0a01eab2f5367cca4a","tid":1633913,"uid":247845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />休息政府會話蒙面法有用"},{"pid":"63267d79641d25ec1b523c8d4aa43be9d2a82e4f","tid":1633913,"uid":26015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c20547b2d11900cecabd1d0a01eab2f5367cca4a","tid":1633913,"uid":247845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />休息政府會話蒙面法有用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:56:06.000Z","msg":"其實龍門任佢罷<br />\n<br />\n休息就話蒙面有用<br />\n唔休息就話加辣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01006489849a5a9b5f12bafe1873898115166e88","tid":1633913,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:57:39.000Z","msg":"係時候休息，暫停裝修，和理非全面進場<br />\nsolomon yue唔撐暴力示威，唔係唔搞，只係等多幾日等條人權法過左先再搞<br />\n班mon post狗挑釁緊你地做激進行動，敵擁我反<br />\n<br />\n黎黎去去都係果幾味"},{"pid":"1a13cde9ba3b038e3698c0b56288fea04c4cbedb","tid":1633913,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:11:30.000Z","msg":"P牌投唔到反對，<br />\n林鄭咁急將所有野推向極致，<br />\n配合 無警時份 同埋 cctvb報導，就係要令我地喺國際上顯得暴力，以及難以接收所有資訊嘅淺黃大眾同前線割蓆（佢自己都開到聲），<br />\n所以我地要做嘅唔係跟佢節奏行，係自己調節返我地嘅節奏。<br />\n<br />\n就係和理乜，唔使同佢急，留住淺黃大眾嘅心，再加以解釋各種行為。獅鳥同裝修呢兩個星期進步得好快，喺人地心目中未有一個既定形象，所以要不斷解釋，營造返一個「示威者只會以武制暴，絕不撩起事端」嘅形象。你要知道並唔係人人都會好似深黃咁追貼所有事，你要同淺黃講先得架，咁樣先可以拉近返大家嘅距離，到時做乜都唔割啦真係。<br />\n<br />\n做乜都好，等人權法過左先。我係認為人權法只係輔助，要贏終需靠我地人民，但大家唔係好想制裁班高官架咩，我地要不息一切要佢地留喺大灣區嘛，即使係要減低裝修力度幾日。"},{"pid":"2641f555db2d060819f38fcbec6df7e83271310b","tid":1633913,"uid":89530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:20:13.000Z","msg":"好老實，三日連假前出招，似係想亂多啲，加上呢兩日有啲平時唔會見到嘅風向係咁鼓吹出去暴力，叫手足打埋記者都有人講，呢一種配合，好難唔令人懷疑。人權法案在即先嚟搞啲咁嘅嘢，亦明顯見到對面想利用暴力情況嚟打亂國際聲援，政府越係想我哋做，我哋越要唔做，抗爭要武但都要文，將近排弱咗嘅文宣做返強，社會民生問題全部推返落政府到，前幾日嘅擠提已經可以大做文章。"},{"pid":"03e8a53ac505e6b3e332515a915e01ab5b1d8c8d","tid":1633913,"uid":157584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96fdd4b1bd02df9650933fafe36bc7b94eef1bad","tid":1633913,"uid":26015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:45:47.000Z","msg":"星期五用緊急法<br />\n接著落黎三日假期 <br />\n其中兩日叫人休息<br />\n目的顯而易見<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就係想大家消化哂緊急法、冷卻之前既憤怒情緒</span></span><br />\n<br />\n講真 如果林奠係今日先宣布用緊急法<br />\n聽日肯定全世界罷工唔撚柒做都似<br />\n佢就係正正唔想見到咁<br />\n就希望大家休息下冷靜下<br />\n聽日繼續如常乖乖咁做港奴 <br />\n唔想你地搞咁多野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />認同<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反對"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:26:39.000Z","msg":"休息唔等同係屋企<br />\n<br />\n個個同我食完飯街坊look落街散步減肥 <br />\n做運動 行樓梯 政府建議市民每日一萬步<br />\n唔好令袋 銀包電話鎖鑰 踢拖 唔好帶口罩 <br />\n廢時比人懷疑 冇宵禁請帶埋屋企小朋友大朋友出街 <br />\n出來散步不犯法 廣傳 唔可以怕 要防止警察犯罪<br />\n<br />\n警察失控事件簿 2019.10.06 大埔 新興橋<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632156\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632156</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}